# Reviewed 2026-07-22 by Alden — Security Scan stage
#
# All 5 findings are in npm's own bundled dependencies inside the
# node:22-slim base image (node-tar, brace-expansion, glob, minimatch).
# They are NOT in our application code (frontend/app/node_modules is clean)
# and are not reachable at runtime — the container runs Express, never npm.
# Cannot be patched without upstream updating the base image.
# Bumping 18 -> 22 already cleared all Debian OS CVEs (14 -> 0).
# Re-review when node:24-slim ships a patched npm.

CVE-2026-13149
CVE-2026-33671
CVE-2026-48815
CVE-2026-59873
